{"tid":1820125,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【邊個夠佢紅】馬蹄露斥哈囉喂導演借她提升知名度：自卑誘發妄想自大","createTime":"2020-01-11T10:50:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T12:38:38.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"158a2a4f8c6efbb2184fafcc3da3aa93403530a0","tid":1820125,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T10:50:59.000Z","msg":"海洋公園去年10月舉行的哈囉喂活動《地獄巨星賀台慶》，因內容涉及政治及敏感時事話題，負責節目的導演兼男主角黃湛深最後「被辭演」。撐警馬蹄露也曾就此事於微博發文譴責海洋公園推卸責任及包庇黃湛深，直指《地獄巨星賀台慶》內容與反修例風波有關，力斥表演是宣傳港獨，煽動仇警，又謂：「將黃媒失實、虛假嘅報道，公然在劇場上演，灌輸、煽動、仇恨給小朋友及家長！簡直是無法無天！」之後她還留言叫網民不要去。<br />\n<br />\n日前馬蹄露再在微博出post鬧黃湛深，她轉貼了黃湛深facebook截圖及其個人照，其中FB截圖，正是黃湛深分享本報「馬蹄露成功進軍大灣區拍戲 貴妃造型好驚嚇」報道，黃湛深並留言：「大灣區嘅觀眾有福啦，當日你篤我灰嘅仇我遲早會報！」<br />\n<br />\n馬蹄露貼出截圖之餘，更留言：「這位黄湛深在臉書揚言會找我報仇！飯碗是你自己打的，怎樣算也算不到我頭上！你的黃絲港獨思想呈現在海洋公園萬聖節的劇場裏，遭入場觀眾的家長向海洋公園投訴，及後傳媒也大肆報道，我只是轉發傳媒的報道而已，你有膽量便找海洋公園或傳媒記者報仇！只有懦夫才會欺負或找女人報仇，不要替他蹭熱度，他正在沾沾自喜話多謝我，還說我是抽他水而蹭熱，自卑誘發妄想自大。」<br />\n<br />\n咁又係，撐警馬蹄露去年10月跟反修例示威者爆衝突時被「私了」受傷，即時變成中國民族英雄，獲中共喉舌《人民日報》在微博高度表揚，跟成龍、梁家輝、譚詠麟、鍾鎮濤齊名，今時今日馬蹄露聲價十級跳，又何需借他人提高知名度！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200111/large/1578733118_bbc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200111%2Flarge%2F1578733118_bbc3.jpg&h=86d28509&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200111/large/1578733118_3b34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200111%2Flarge%2F1578733118_3b34.jpg&h=4775cf82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200111/large/1578733162_2efe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200111%2Flarge%2F1578733162_2efe.jpg&h=9afc30bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200111/large/1578733406_69be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200111%2Flarge%2F1578733406_69be.jpg&h=df1deb5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20200111/60474344\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200111%2F60474344&d=E2fLMnMY5FLAMirJUdBaWakErG%2BwP2VMcW32eObqVUU%3D&h=7ecf6521\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200111%2F60474344&h=24cd2448\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20200111/60474344</a>"},{"pid":"4d67a3a11925f357c394c49236566ae061895671","tid":1820125,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T10:51:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=E2fLMnMY5FLAMirJUdBaWakErG%2BwP2VMcW32eObqVUU%3D&h=17851040\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"ebcd8456c945d7669e0ea693af496ae2ed2e934d","tid":1820125,"uid":228437,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T10:55:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">講還講唔好貼相</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"4bdcd419c83cb953bca9019e8d52f809632e3f12","tid":1820125,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T10:56:27.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[全港最大的Fact Check平台-非食店篇]集合超過400間各地區各行業的良心店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1817378\" data-auto-link target=